				\begin{document}$$x_{ij} \in \left\{ {0,1,2} \right\}$$\end{document}xij∈0,1,2 is the additively coded allele frequency of the ith marker for the jth individual, S is a set of SNP’s that survived the clumping and thresholding steps, t is one of the two traits studied as base phenotypes, and \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
